00:00:44.406 --> 00:00:46.530
But beyond that, there are
other interesting things

00:00:46.530 --> 00:00:47.655
in the Harvard Square area.

00:00:47.655 --> 00:00:52.260
Brattle Street, an old street,
has been rich for a long time,

00:00:52.260 --> 00:00:53.575
