00:00:56.670 --> 00:00:58.530
I'm always curious to
know, what happened

00:00:58.530 --> 00:01:00.150
to them after the revolution,
why were they there

00:01:00.150 --> 00:01:02.358
in the first place, why were
they in Cambridge rather

00:01:02.358 --> 00:01:04.450
than Boston, things like this.

00:01:04.450 --> 00:01:07.590
So the architectural history
and the history of the region,

00:01:07.590 --> 00:01:09.270
of the area, tells
us a lot about

00:01:09.270 --> 00:01:11.130
the social, economic,
and political history

00:01:11.130 --> 00:01:12.517
of the area as well.

00:01:12.517 --> 00:01:14.850
And I believe Charlie's also
going to be talking, today,

00:01:14.850 --> 00:01:17.880
about some of the development
