00:02:27.690 --> 00:02:32.460
And what you get
is a hefty volume.

00:02:32.460 --> 00:02:38.490
So I thought that I would talk
to you a little bit about who

00:02:38.490 --> 00:02:42.150
the Historical Commission
is and what it does.

00:02:42.150 --> 00:02:45.540
And then Charlie's going
to introduce the book

00:02:45.540 --> 00:02:48.820
and talk some about
